MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

93-636. Cook v. Wineberry Deli, Inc.

Summit County, No. 15694. This cause is pending before the court as a discretionary appeal. Upon consideration of the joint application for dismissal, with prejudice,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the joint application for dismissal, with prejudice, be, and the same is hereby, granted, effective July 27, 1994.
